 1846 it was a suffragan diocese of the [[Patriarch of Venice]].<ref name=CathHierUdine>[http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/diocese/dudin.html "Archdiocese of Udine"] ''[[Catholic-Hierarchy.org]]''. David M. Cheney. Retrieved October 7, 2016</ref> <ref name=GCathUdine>[http://www.gcatholic.org/dioceses/diocese/udin0.htm "Metropolitan Archdiocese of Udine"] ''GCatholic.org''. Gabriel Chow. Retrieved October 7, 2016</ref>
